    <div class="page-feature-grid">
      <div class="page-feature"><div class="page-feature-title">AI Not Functional</div><div class="page-feature-body">Outputs were pre-designed for the prototype. Real AI implementation requires ongoing tuning and validation.</div></div>
      <div class="page-feature"><div class="page-feature-title">Real-Time Data Simulated</div><div class="page-feature-body">Wait times and ride data were placeholder values — live integration with park systems was out of scope.</div></div>
      <div class="page-feature"><div class="page-feature-title">Partnership Risk</div><div class="page-feature-body">Revenue model depends on local business adoption. Early stage vendors may decline or have limited data.</div></div>
